<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">أهـ ب:</span> <span class="c2">(تَأَهَّبَ)</span> اسْتَعَدَّ وَ <span class="c2">(أُهْبَةُ)</span> الْحَرْبِ عِدَّتُهَا وَجَمْعُهَا <span class="c2">(أُهَبٌ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(الْإِهَابُ)</span> الْجِلْدُ مَا لَمْ يُدْبَغْ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>